{"tid":1760604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蝙蝠女手持汽油彈激嬲中國網軍　DC刪圖又被轟向人民幣服務","createTime":"2019-11-28T10:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T16:47:25.000Z","uid":69753,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2eb205c8f53f204e243ac7dbc14b8bc2340848a","tid":1760604,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201911/78597567_2490193024595224_735723710211686400_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201911%2F78597567_2490193024595224_735723710211686400_n.jpg&h=02081778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑衣蝙蝠女手持汽油彈，寫著「The future is young（未來是年輕人的），這一幅於DC社交網站上載的圖片，成為了中國網軍的攻擊目標，最終DC刪圖了事。 <br />\n<br />\nDC漫畫《蝙蝠俠：黑暗騎士歸來》即將於下月出版續集《The Golden Child》，近日於社交網站上載了宣傳圖，見到蝙蝠女高舉已點燃的汽油彈，隨即被轉貼到微博世界。 <br />\n<br />\n中國網民見到畫面之後，就解讀為「撐港」，隨即「出兵」到DC的Instagram留言，留言間出現了大量殘體字。 <br />\n<br />\nDC刪圖之後，又有另一批網民到其他DC貼文留言，批評刪圖決定是討好中國。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-28-2019/57901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-28-2019%2F57901&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=4bd26c7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-28-2019/57901</a><br />\n- Copyright  2019<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不愧係猶太人公司"},{"pid":"88c9cdcbe79f34e26a91f22722a60457b91bb5c3","tid":1760604,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d9ba9170dac1fdab6a4fff2a78e4672f8d1b48","tid":1760604,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"2a4f0e316a3dc6d04f697bdd924f6434869f9b23","tid":1760604,"uid":69753,"lik